Hp = (1d10 + constitutionModifier) * level
Combat rule: 
           1. Attack Roll(attacker): d20 + attackBonus
           2. Armor Class(enemy) = 10 + Dexterity modifier
           3. If Attack Roll > AC attack successful!
                 else attack fail!
           4. Damage score = 1d8 + damage bonus
           5. enemy's Hp minus damage score step by step
Attack bonus =   Strength Modifier (melee weapon)
                 Dexterity Modifier (ranged weapon)
Damage bonus =   Strength Modifier
Ability Modifier =   [(Ability scores - 10)/2]
Ability Score = Base ability scores(4d6) + gained ability score         